name: Super Bunner Bros.
description:
Here is the link to the game:

http://rebirth-gayme-jam.herokuapp.com

...also included is a game design document.

For this game all members decided to step out of their comfort zones. A multiplayer browser experience is a first for all of us, and it's not easy. The goal was very ambitious and ended up breaching the scope of the 12 hour timeline. The game is still a work in progress.
